%h2 Overview
%p Pain and stress are signals: if it doesn’t need to be done, then don’t do it!
%p The question then becomes: does it need to be done?

%table
  %tr
    %th
    %th.left It needs to be done
    %th.left It doesn’t need to be done
  %tr
    %th.right You do it
    %td.left
      and stop when you feel satisfied.
      %span.control Control¹
    %td.left
      but never feel satisfied.
      %span.compulsion Compulsion⁴
  %tr
    %th.right You don&rsquo;t do it
    %td.left
      and never feel ready.
      %span.guilt Guilt²
    %td.left
      but start when you feel ready.
      %span.serenity Serenity³

%p
  The goal of BipolarType is to maximize
  %span.control control¹
  and
  %span.serenity serenity³
  and minimize
  %span.guilt guilt²
  and
